{"Title":"淡奶油酸奶的做法","Primary":["纯牛奶450克","淡奶油50克"],"Auxiliary":["酸奶菌粉1支"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.做酸奶的保温盒和汤匙，用开水烫一下消毒","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142258398308823.jpg","2.将酸奶菌粉倒入保温盒中","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142258399182468.jpg","3.倒入450克牛奶","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142258400040840.jpg","4.再加入50克淡奶油","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142258401596474.jpg","5.用汤匙把原材料搅拌均匀","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142258402077171.jpg","6.在酸奶机中加入温水","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142258402493704.jpg","7.保温盒盖上盖子，放入酸奶机里，通上电源","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142258402975798.jpg","8.8小时左右打开盖子，酸奶凝结即可","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142258403408891.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142258410622505.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142258410886249.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142258411119849.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142258411322455.jpg","烹饪技巧","1、所有用具要用洗净，用开水烫一下消毒；2、加了淡奶油，比平时做酸奶需要的时间短，可以提前看下，凝结了就好。"]}